   Welcome to NEED  
 
    
  The mission of the NEED Project is to promote an energy conscious and educated society by creating effective networks of students, educators, business, government and community leaders to design and deliver objective, multi-sided energy education programs. NEED works with energy companies, agencies and organizations to bring balanced energy programs to the nation's schools with a focus on strong teacher professional development, timely and balanced curriculum materials, signature program capabilities and turn-key program management.  NEED Quick Links      Calculate the cost of your Thanksgiving Meal!     2011 NEED Annual Report  (Released June 22, 2011) - Financial Statements, the 2011 NEED Youth Awards Winning Projects and Program Spotlights  The  2011-2012 Resource Catalog  contains information about NEED products and services, order forms, and information about ordering specific pieces of NEED's hands-on kits.               
    
 
  

 

     
 

  
  
      
     

	 
	     
	
	
		   

	
	
	     
	 
	

     
 
 
      
     

	 
		      
		      
		      	
